Articles.Content: It will slowly lower it's orbit over the next few days to 200km. Now that it is in lunar orbit it will conduct tests in preparation for CE-5, take HD close up images of the landing site and perform rendezvous and docking with a virtual target in March and April. After that is unsure, maybe it will fly into deep space or rendezvous with another asteroid, or maybe it will become an L-2 communication sat.
All procedures complete, the probe now has an orbital period of 127 minutes.
